description:
This is a compilation of videos by Hector Garcia, CPA / Twitter: @QBKAccounting and other freely published videos by the best QuickBooks Online experts such as:

  • Woody Adams from Intuit and The QB Show / Twitter: @qbclay
  • MB Ramondi, CPA

You will learn the basics of getting started with QuickBooks Online, plus:

  1. Converting from QuickBooks Desktop & Comparing features
  2. Navigations Tips and Tricks
  3. Importing Bank Transactions / Bank Feeds
  4. Troubleshooting and how to fix common mistakes
  5. Other Advanced Topics





Free Coupon, for the ones that read: QBO IS AWESOME (No Spaces)
title: Master QuickBooks Online (QBO)
